      <title>杂谈：为什么在当今的世界我们仍应该使用非即时性媒体</title>
      <link href="/2025/02/08/%E6%9D%82%E8%B0%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%BB%8D%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93/"/>
      <url>/2025/02/08/%E6%9D%82%E8%B0%88%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E4%BB%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%BB%8D%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%9D%9E%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="非即时性媒体是什么">非即时性媒体是什么</h3><p>奈何本人并没有对这方面进行深入研究<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>这个词语也是我自己想出来的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>并非专业名词<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p>非即时性媒体<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>就是用户在使用该媒体时所获得的反馈并非是非即时的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span>那么即时性媒体<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>一定不需要我过多叙述</p><p>但注意<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>上文中提到的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>反馈<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span>与<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>即时<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span>都是指广义上的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>反馈<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span>与<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-end"><h-inner>“</h-inner></h-char></span>即时<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>”</h-inner></h-char></span></p><h3 id="生活中的-非 / 即时性媒体">生活中的 非 / 即时性媒体</h3><p>说到即时性媒体<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>我们不难举出一些例子<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span>抖音<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>快手<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>电话<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>…                                                                                                                                 例子中的电话不难理解<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>而我为什么把抖音<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>快手也列入其中呢<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>？</h-inner></h-char></span>这两个软件看似是用户的主动选择<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>获取信息的工具<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>实则不然<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>随着你不断刷视频<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>作为用户的你就不断被打上标签<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>这些软件便会把你想看到的东西推荐给你<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>这样的反馈便是即时的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>因为他们<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>你的情绪在这些媒体中不断获得反馈<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>于是不断强化<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span>综上<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>我们可以知道抖音快手是即时性媒体</p><p>而非即时性媒体往往是我们忘记或者被淡出视野的东西<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>：</h-inner></h-char></span>论坛<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>社区<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>博客<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>邮件<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p><h3 id="现状">现状</h3><p>而现状是<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>即时性媒体充斥<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>渗透在生活的各个方面中<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>而非即时性媒体却逐渐被淡出人们的视野<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>这不是个好现象<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p>即时性媒体固然方便<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>但当他逐渐占据非即时性媒体的地位时<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>危险就出现了<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span>人们的情绪不断被激化<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>形成了一群群非黑即白的极端者<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>不同想法的人无法和睦的相处<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>沟通消失了<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>因为行为的反馈实在是过于即时<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>沟通所带来的情绪反馈显然没有争吵和冲突所带来的情绪反馈强烈<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p><p>潜移默化的<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>这导致人们的思想变局限<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>情绪容易被激化<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>事物会被放大或缩小<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>难以看清事件的全貌</p><h3 id="我们仍应该使用非即时性媒体">我们仍应该使用非即时性媒体</h3><p>我想<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>我们没有办法消除这些即时性媒体<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>而应该平衡好非/即时性媒体的关系<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span>多反思自己<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>审视自己<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>使用甚至更多的使用非即时性媒体<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span>可以让我们更多的从互联网中受益<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>，</h-inner></h-char></span>减少我们在互联网中受到的伤害<span class="bd-box"><h-char class="bd bd-beg"><h-inner>。</h-inner></h-char></span></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
